{"tid":912761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家樂肥鼠午市直墮食客碗中","createTime":"2018-11-23T02:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T05:47:35.000Z","uid":41404,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"07a26241e50562a5ea73223868634492339fcae6","tid":912761,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T02:26:04.000Z","msg":"大媽天不怕，地不怕，但可能最怕老鼠。有網民指，大家樂觀塘樂華分店昨日（22日）中午，有一隻肥大的老鼠從天花直墮食客碗中，嚇得大媽也高聲叫喊。據《蘋果》了解，職員也承認昨午有老鼠「光顧」，但強調該店過往未試過有鼠蹤，職員已將老鼠連同有關餐具一併棄置，並即時消毒該處。<br />\n<br />\n網民李寶寶昨午在「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」facebook專頁上載照片，指接近下午1時，到樂華大家樂午膳時，「食食吓突然跌隻好可愛嘅比卡超落嚟，有大嬸超大聲叫，女經理好快走出嚟，但都俾我打完卡（影相放上網）先拎走（老鼠）」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181123/58944455\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F58944455&d=QaamyzB5xWbHQotOHZxTl7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=c0bf130b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F58944455&h=20184987\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181123/58944455</a>"},{"pid":"1152fa82af9057463ab5a8d757cc378d0ea20b52","tid":912761,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T02:27:21.000Z","msg":"擺盤？"},{"pid":"06f7f2e46e490180a7dc8312349db4c502f7c062","tid":912761,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T02:28:56.000Z","msg":"免費加料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ef7361afdba5b52ce0182b6d957d594a877c55","tid":912761,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T02:32:08.000Z","msg":"隻老鼠跌死咗？"},{"pid":"a595ac1e673cda49d7d587a862b98bbc4ea01a2c","tid":912761,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci